Part 10: Concurrency

10.1 Actors

```pascal
actor Counter {
    var _count: iso int32 := 0
    
    behavior increment()
    begin
        _count += 1
    end
    
    function get(): val int32
    begin
        return _count as val
    end
}
```

10.2 Channels

