Part 16: Compiler Implementation

16.1 Self-Hosting Pipeline

```yaml
self_hosting_pipeline:
  phase_0: "Zig → Maia (bootstrap compiler)"
  phase_0_5: "Zig → Koda (bootstrap VM)"
  phase_1: "Maia (bootstrap) → Maia (self-hosted)"
  phase_1_5: "Maia (self-hosted) → Standard Library"
  phase_2: "Maia (self-hosted) → Koda VM (rewrite)"
  phase_3: "Koda (on Maia VM) → Koda Standard Library"

final_state:
  maia: "Compiles itself (no Zig)"
  koda: "Runs on Maia VM (no Zig)"
